{"tid":1634901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人既歷史敵人從沒改變 : 港共中共 (附送文宣)","createTime":"2019-10-07T10:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T13:17:56.000Z","uid":298324,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"56af5f95fbb8e0afb40c538674ef17bb9a1648e5","tid":1634901,"uid":298324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:40:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人歷史上既敵人從來都係港共同中共。</span><br />\n<br />\n1967年，中共系大陸進行文化大革命之際，港共發動六七暴動企圖奪權香港管治權，有幸港英果斷防衛以及廣大香港人對之孤立既情況下，港共終歸敗北。<br />\n<br />\n2019年，超過50年過去，時移世易。發動暴動既左派暴徒，當年燒死電台主持，炸死北角兩姊弟，如今成為香港管治集團既成員。50多年前反對動用緊急法既大公報，今日舉腳讚成。原因無他 - 中共同港共已經牢牢掌握香港既管治權，變成大家既統治者。<br />\n<br />\n希望巴絲認清黑警、紅資、逃犯條例，甚至林鄭背後既終極大佬。<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人既歷史天敵，從沒改變。</span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">港匪不兩立!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">We Beat 'Em Before...We'll Beat 'Em Again!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8cLUhHK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8cLUhHK.jpg&h=9105e8fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0JPaAuq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0JPaAuq.jpg&h=7f2d6f1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rdtuQ2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrdtuQ2M.jpg&h=dc45e5dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9QLw4nN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9QLw4nN.jpg&h=affcf472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCcSOPt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCcSOPt.jpg&h=fae49360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZwxLpnP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZwxLpnP.jpg&h=aedf8f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eUcjtPv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeUcjtPv.jpg&h=431d5d39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rOsfMA2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrOsfMA2.jpg&h=4ab24785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Du51G9m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDu51G9m.jpg&h=7a040957&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c61e21e82532fc975bff42c50ea36bc08c6abeb2","tid":1634901,"uid":298324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:45:38.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"caf5a02e6769702629e77ec2007fa48203fd9f84","tid":1634901,"uid":77872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:45:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dfbcc908f356411085df8a9c1fb7ad755bb0f983","tid":1634901,"uid":287755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:23:01.000Z","msg":"高質"},{"pid":"f34559e981e98f095dcc0a28c7af00b58d4c39d2","tid":1634901,"uid":21336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:12:47.000Z","msg":"Pushing hard"},{"pid":"efb99e153a90374d9460bd2b3b6137e3b2cf46b4","tid":1634901,"uid":21336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:13:36.000Z","msg":"要送上twitter!"},{"pid":"61c9bd19b93e15cb72c32b65ef128151293be932","tid":1634901,"uid":270323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}